<page>
   <topic>A5_DEFINE_GLOBAL_VARS Function</topic>
   <description>Brings up a dialog box to define Global Variables</description>

   <syntax>C a5_define_global_vars()</syntax>  
    <discussion>
The A5_DEFINE_GLOBAL_VARS() function displays the Global Variables dialog box, which allows you to edit, add, or delete global variables.
   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
a5_define_global_vars()
]]></example>

   
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
